                <div class="info-box-header">          
                    附註
                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    <span lang="en-US">(1): Snakes of the Agkistrodon Complex, A Monographic Review; Howard K. Gloyd and Roger Connant. SSAR. 1990. Page 388</span>.        
                </div>
            </div>

